---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Child Safety & Protection Policy - Boomger."
  slug="guideline"
  description="Boomger is fully committed to preventing and combating Child Sexual Abuse and Exploitation (CSAE) in all forms."
>
  <main
    class="pt-10 pb-24 mx-6 sm:mx-12 lg:mx-24 max-w-5xl text-zinc-900 leading-relaxed"
  >
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">
        📄 Child Safety & Protection Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
        App: <span class="font-semibold">Boomger</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Developer: Boomger Limited</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section -->
    <div class="space-y-7">
      <!-- 1 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
          🔒 Commitment to Child Safety
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          Boomger is fully committed to preventing and combating Child Sexual
          Abuse and Exploitation (CSAE) in all forms.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-3">
          Our platform strictly prohibits any activity, content, or behavior
          that involves:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Sexual exploitation or abuse of minors</li>
          <li>Grooming or predatory behavior</li>
          <li>Sharing or promoting Child Sexual Abuse Material (CSAM)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3 font-medium text-red-600">
          We maintain a zero-tolerance policy for violations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
          🚫 Age Restriction (18+ Only)
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-3">Boomger is intended strictly for adults.</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Users must be at least 18 years old to access or use the app</li>
          <li>We actively take steps to prevent minors from registering</li>
          <li>Any account suspected to belong to a minor will be:</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-10 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-700">
          <li>Suspended immediately</li>
          <li>Permanently removed after verification</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
          🛡️ Prohibited Content & Behavior
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-3">The following are strictly prohibited on Boomger:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Any form of child sexual exploitation or abuse</li>
          <li>Uploading, sharing, or distributing CSAM</li>
          <li>Attempting to contact or engage minors</li>
          <li>
            Any predatory, exploitative, or inappropriate behavior toward minors
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-4 font-medium">Violations will result in:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2 text-red-600">
          <li>Immediate account termination</li>
          <li>Possible reporting to law enforcement authorities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 4 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">🔍 Monitoring & Enforcement</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We use a combination of:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Automated detection systems</li>
          <li>User reporting tools</li>
          <li>Human moderation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">to identify and remove harmful content or users.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          We continuously improve our safety systems to ensure compliance with
          global child protection standards.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 5 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">
          📢 Reporting & Contact Information
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          If you encounter any content or behavior related to child exploitation
          or unsafe activity, report it immediately.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-semibold mb-2">📧 Designated Child Safety Contact:</p>
          <p>
            Email: <a href="mailto:support@boomger.com" class="text-blue-600"
              >support@boomger.com</a
            >
          </p>
          <p>
            Phone: <a href="tel:+12048906706" class="text-blue-600"
              >+1 204 890 6706</a
            >
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-3">All reports are handled urgently and confidentially.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Boomger cooperates with relevant authorities in investigating
          CSAE-related incidents where required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 6 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">🌐 Compliance with Policies</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">Boomger complies with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Google Play Child Safety Standards</li>
          <li>Applicable international laws on child protection</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          We are committed to maintaining a safe and secure environment for all
          users.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 7 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">🔄 Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>This policy may be updated periodically to reflect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
          <li>Legal or regulatory changes</li>
          <li>Improvements in safety practices</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">Users are encouraged to review this page regularly.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
